<p><b>PmWiki</b> is <a href="/wiki/Free_software" title="Free software">free</a> <a href="/wiki/Wiki_software" title="Wiki software">wiki software</a> written by Patrick R. Michaud in the <a href="/wiki/PHP" title="PHP">PHP</a> programming language. It is licensed under the terms of the <a href="/wiki/GNU_General_Public_License" title="GNU General Public License">GNU General Public License</a>.</p>
